  <bioghist id="aspace_ee4d63efb33a29a64a4859aaa28e8e65">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Member of the Class of 1994. Member of the Cornell Fencing Team, 1990-1994; Captain, 1992-1994; Assistant Coach, 1994-1995. One of nine female athletes to bring a Title IX lawsuit against Cornell in 1993 after the Women's Fencing and Gymnastics teams were cut. The teams were reinstated in December 1993.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_a8c72f403add4ac2569a5683cc568546">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Team schedules, brochures, captain?s letters, newspaper clippings, programs, and ephemera from the Cornell Varsity Fencing team from 1990-1997. Includes press releases, correspondence, and newspaper clippings about the Title IX lawsuit brought against Cornell University by members of the Women?s Fencing and Gymnastics teams.</p>  </scopecontent>
